{"prompt": "Develop a comprehensive portal for a healthcare staffing agency. The primary color should be a muted teal.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Healthcare Staffing Solutions</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #4f7f7f;\n            --secondary-color: #e0e8e8;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --white-color: #ffffff;\n            --font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-family: var(--font-family);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--white-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--white-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: var(--white-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-color);\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .card {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 20px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .card h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n\n        form label {\n            display: block;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        form input[type=\"text\"],\n        form input[type=\"email\"],\n        form textarea,\n        form button {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-family: var(--font-family);\n        }\n\n        form button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--white-color);\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n\n        form button:hover {\n            background-color: #3e6666;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--white-color);\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Healthcare Staffing Solutions</h1>\n        <p>Connecting Skilled Professionals with Leading Healthcare Facilities</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#services\">Our Services</a>\n        <a href=\"#careers\">Careers</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact Us</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>We are a premier healthcare staffing agency dedicated to providing high-quality, reliable, and compassionate healthcare professionals to hospitals, clinics, long-term care facilities, and other healthcare organizations. Our mission is to ensure that every patient receives the best possible care by matching talented individuals with the right opportunities.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"services\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"card\">\n                <h3>Temporary Staffing</h3>\n                <p>Quickly fill short-term staffing needs with experienced nurses, technicians, and support staff.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"card\">\n                <h3>Permanent Placement</h3>\n                <p>Find the perfect long-term fit for your organization with our comprehensive recruitment process.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"card\">\n                <h3>Specialized Recruitment</h3>\n                <p>We cater to niche healthcare roles, ensuring you find experts in areas like ICU, ER, Pediatrics, and more.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"careers\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Careers for Healthcare Professionals</h2>\n            <p>Are you a dedicated healthcare professional looking for your next opportunity? We partner with reputable facilities to offer a wide range of rewarding positions. Explore our current openings and take the next step in your career.</p>\n            <div class=\"card\">\n                <h3>Why Work With Us?</h3>\n                <ul>\n                    <li>Competitive pay and benefits</li>\n                    <li>Flexible scheduling options</li>\n                    <li>Access to exclusive job opportunities</li>\n                    <li>Dedicated career support</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n            <a href=\"#contact\"><button>View Openings</button></a>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Contact Us</h2>\n            <p>Whether you're looking to hire staff or seeking a new role, we're here to help. Get in touch with us today!</p>\n            <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                <label for=\"name\">Name:</label>\n                <input type=\"text\" id=\"name\" name=\"name\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"email\">Email:</label>\n                <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n\n                <label for=\"message\">Message:</label>\n                <textarea id=\"message\" name=\"message\" rows=\"4\" required></textarea>\n\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Healthcare Staffing Solutions. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>"}